<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="bg-yellow-100 dark:bg-yellow-900/30 rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6 leading-relaxed">
    <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-3">È possibile <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">dividere</strong>:</p>
    <ul class="space-y-2">
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <span class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold mr-2">•</span>
        <span class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">la <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">vocale iniziale</strong> di parola, seguita da consonante (<strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">i-so-la</strong>);</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <span class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold mr-2">•</span>
        <span class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">le consonanti <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">doppie</strong> (<strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">pat-ti-ni</strong>);</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <span class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold mr-2">•</span>
        <span class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">il gruppo <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">cq</strong> (<strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">ac-qua</strong>);</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <span class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold mr-2">•</span>
        <span class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200"><strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">l</strong>, <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">r</strong>, <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">m</strong>, <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">n</strong> dalla consonante che le segue (<strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">el-mo, por-ta</strong>).</span>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-3 mt-4"><strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">Non</strong> è possibile <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">dividere</strong>:</p>
    <ul class="space-y-2">
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <span class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold mr-2">•</span>
        <span class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">la lettera <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">s</strong> dalla consonante che la segue (<strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">po-sti-no</strong>);</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start">
        <span class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold mr-2">•</span>
        <span class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200"><strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">gl</strong>, <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">ch</strong>, <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">gh</strong>, <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">gli</strong>, <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">sc</strong>, <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">gn</strong> (<strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">fi-glio, chia-ro, ghi-ro</strong>).</span>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mt-4">
      Se ci sono due o tre vocali vicine nella stessa parola, ricorda che<br>
      quasi sempre stanno insieme. Se hai dubbi, consulta il dizionario.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6 border-4 border-yellow-400 dark:border-yellow-600">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
      <span class="bg-blue-800 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      <span class="bg-yellow-400 dark:bg-yellow-600 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200 px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
      <span>Dividi in sillabe le parole di ogni gruppo. Osserva gli esempi.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
      <% exercise_1_groups = [
        {
          items: [
            { word: "cassetto", example: "cas/set/to" },
            { word: "passaggio", answer: "pas/sag/gio" },
            { word: "acquazzone", answer: "ac/quaz/zo/ne" }
          ]
        },
        {
          items: [
            { word: "costola", example: "co/sto/la" },
            { word: "palestra", answer: "pa/le/stra" },
            { word: "maschera", answer: "ma/sche/ra" }
          ]
        },
        {
          items: [
            { word: "calcoli", example: "cal/co/li" },
            { word: "pentola", answer: "pen/to/la" },
            { word: "cartina", answer: "car/ti/na" }
          ]
        },
        {
          items: [
            { word: "coprire", example: "co/pri/re" },
            { word: "metrico", answer: "me/tri/co" },
            { word: "bruchi", answer: "bru/chi" }
          ]
        },
        {
          items: [
            { word: "cognome", example: "co/gno/me" },
            { word: "famiglia", answer: "fa/mi/glia" },
            { word: "miscelare", answer: "mi/sce/la/re" }
          ]
        },
        {
          items: [
            { word: "elica", example: "e/li/ca" },
            { word: "amaca", answer: "a/ma/ca" },
            { word: "umido", answer: "u/mi/do" }
          ]
        }
      ] %>

      <% exercise_1_groups.each do |group| %>
        <div class="space-y-2 sm:ml-7">
          <% group[:items].each do |item| %>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold mr-2">•</span>
              <span class="w-32 md:w-40 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200"><%= item[:word] %></span>
              <% if item[:example] %>
                <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold w-32 md:w-40 text-left"><%= item[:example] %></span>
              <% else %>
                <input type="text"
                       class="border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white w-32 md:w-40 text-left focus:outline-none"
                       data-fill-blanks-target="input"
                       data-correct-answer="<%= item[:answer] %>">
              <% end %>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2 -->
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-pink-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">2</span>
      Quando spezzi una parola per <strong class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400">andare a capo</strong> devi considerare la divisione in sillabe. Per ogni parola, indica almeno due punti in cui potresti spezzarla. Osserva l'esempio.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:ml-7">
        <span class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold mr-2">•</span>
        <span class="w-32 md:w-40 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">pasticcio</span>
        <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold">pa/sticcio - pastic/cio</span>
      </div>

      <% exercise_2_words = [
        { word: "cocomero", answer: "co/comero - coco/mero" },
        { word: "pantofole", answer: "pan/tofole - panto/fole" },
        { word: "panettone", answer: "pa/nettone - panet/tone" },
        { word: "chimica", answer: "chi/mica" },
        { word: "moscerino", answer: "mo/scerino - mosce/rino" },
        { word: "ruscello", answer: "ru/scello - rusce/llo" },
        { word: "scomparire", answer: "scom/parire - scompa/rire" },
        { word: "bollente", answer: "bol/lente - bollen/te" },
        { word: "larghezza", answer: "lar/ghezza - larghe/zza" }
      ] %>

      <% exercise_2_words.each do |item| %>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:ml-7">
          <span class="text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold mr-2">•</span>
          <span class="w-32 md:w-40 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200"><%= item[:word] %></span>
          <input type="text"
                 class="border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white w-56 md:w-72 text-left focus:outline-none"
                 data-fill-blanks-target="input"
                 data-correct-answer="<%= item[:answer] %>">
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise Controls -->
  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div><!-- chiude space-y-6 -->
</div>
